{"TopicId":135502,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"I wonder why Squad doesn\u0026#039;t want to give us a dV and TWR readout","CreatedByName":"Foxster","CreatedById":113764,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-03-31T12:34:34Z","PageNum":10,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-09T11:08:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222504246\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022135502\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460196036\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289470\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ModZero\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, ModZero said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd, finally, pretty sure you\u0027re trying to argue that KSP is unplayable and nobody ever made orbit in stock.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhere did I say this lol?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was going interplanetary before I knew this game even had mods at all.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you actually have anything serious to add to this discussion?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-09T11:09:27Z\u0022 title=\u002204/09/2016 11:09  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 9, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Rocket In My Pocket\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ModZero","CreatedById":89470,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-09T11:14:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222504296\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022135502\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460200084\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154640\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rocket In My Pocket\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, Rocket In My Pocket said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhere did I say this lol?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s the gist of your argument: \u0022games without\u00A0feature X are inherently broken\u0022. They\u0027re not, and neither is KSP, which is illustrated by:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222504296\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022135502\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460200084\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154640\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rocket In My Pocket\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Rocket In My Pocket said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI was going interplanetary before I knew this game even had mods at all.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n...which I of course knew, because pretty much everyone did, which means\u00A0you\u0027re being not very serious, so:\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222504296\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022135502\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460200084\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022154640\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Rocket In My Pocket\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, Rocket In My Pocket said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDo you actually have anything serious to add to this discussion?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, did you, actually? You just threw a bunch of assertion, each one invalidated by at least one fairly successful game, implying (but skirting, because actually making one\u0027s point clearly would make it too easy for others to dispute you) a point that\u0027s invalidated by your own experience.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nKSP is just fine without dV readings. Many players, including me, would rather have it \u2014 possibly most. But implying the game is broken for not having is, um,\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Enot very nice at all\u003C/em\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-09T11:19:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222504302\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022135502\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460200497\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289470\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ModZero\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nJust now, ModZero said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n-snip-\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLook, it\u0027s clear you want to argue with someone, but that someone isn\u0027t going to be me, sorry.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou\u0027re welcome to go back and read the other posts I\u00A0made in this thread which weren\u0027t as flippant.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222504302\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022135502\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460200497\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289470\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ModZero\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, ModZero said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\num,\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Enot very nice at all\u003C/em\u003E.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWere your feelings hurt? Do you want a hug?\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022true\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-09T11:22:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThat\u0027s quite enough. Please discuss the posts and not the posters, please.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Enceos","CreatedById":110725,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-09T11:31:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/127483-eddiew/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022127483\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/127483-eddiew/\u0022\u003E@eddiew\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/153969-kosmognome/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022153969\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/153969-kosmognome/\u0022\u003E@Kosmognome\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0You can try the beta version here:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/85834-10511-malahs-quick-mods-updated-quickscroll-quickcontracts-quickmute-quicksearch-quickstart-and-quickbrake-20160401/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;embedComment=2477327\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-09T12:13:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222504328\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022135502\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460201489\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110725\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Enceos\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n39 minutes ago, Enceos said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/127483-eddiew/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022127483\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/127483-eddiew/\u0022\u003E@eddiew\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/153969-kosmognome/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022153969\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/153969-kosmognome/\u0022\u003E@Kosmognome\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0You can try the beta version here:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/85834-10511-malahs-quick-mods-updated-quickscroll-quickcontracts-quickmute-quicksearch-quickstart-and-quickbrake-20160401/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0026amp;embedComment=2477327\u0026amp;embedDo=findComment\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooks like the wheel wasn\u0027t reinvented, it\u0027s using KER\u0027s code for the calculations and just displaying the data differently.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPersonally I\u0027d rather the displays attached to the staging display (since it\u0027s already a staging list), but that\u0027s personal preference. Kudos to malah for the stockalike implementation.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"GoSlash27","CreatedById":111526,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-10T00:53:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m one of those folks who prefers to do the math myself. In fact, I take it a step further and let the math dictate my design before I even start building. This is how I am able to optimize my designs for weight and cost without resorting to trial and error in the VAB.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0This is not to say that I think that everyone should be forced to do without a readout (I don\u0027t). I\u0027m just saying that I\u0027m very familiar with the process involved and it would be darn near impossible to implement in- game in a way that avoids incorrect answers.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0As everyone upstream has already said, an in- game DV readout would be tougher to implement than it appears.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBest,\u003Cbr\u003E\n-Slashy\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}